                     <author key="n 79086812" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/56731778/">Ḥāfiẓ, 14th cent.Ḥāfiẓ ShīrāzīShams al-Dīn Muḥammad Shīrāzī‏حافظ شيرازى<addName xml:lang="ar" type="laqab"/>
